table.name: item_qf
table.description: Contains qualification details of an item origin

columns.name: DOMAIN_NAME
columns.description: Database domain where this data is stored.

columns.name: INSERT_USER
columns.description: The user ID of the data insert user.

columns.name: INSERT_DATE
columns.description: Date and time of data insert.

columns.name: UPDATE_USER
columns.description: The user ID of the data update user.

columns.name: UPDATE_DATE
columns.description: Date and time of the most recent data update.

columns.name: ITEM_QF_GID
columns.description: The GID for the item qualification.

columns.name: ITEM_QF_XID
columns.description: The XID for the item qualification.

columns.name: ITEM_ORIGIN_GID
columns.description: The GID for the item origin.

columns.name: DESCRIPTION
columns.description: Describes the item qualification.

columns.name: GTM_TRADE_AGREEMENT_GID
columns.description: The GID for the trade agreement associated with the item qualification.

columns.name: GTM_PROD_CLASS_TYPE_GID
columns.description: The GID for the product classification type of the importing country.

columns.name: CLASSIFICATION_CODE
columns.description: The product classification code associated with the product classification type of the item qualification.

columns.name: IS_QUALIFIED
columns.description: Indicates if an item qualified for a trade agreement. Can have 'Y','N' and 'NS' and default value is 'NS'

columns.name: QF_PREFERENCE_CRITERIA_GID
columns.description: The GID for the preference criteria associated with an item qualification.

columns.name: QF_RVC_METHOD_GID
columns.description: The GID for the regional value content method associated with an item qualification.

columns.name: PRODUCER
columns.description: Indicates if the supplier/partner is the producer of the goods.

columns.name: EFFECTIVE_DATE
columns.description: The effective date for the item qualification.

columns.name: EXPIRATION_DATE
columns.description: The expiration date for the item qualification.

columns.name: STATUS
columns.description: Indicates the status of an item qualification.
